OL,7,FElectric motorcycles and e-scooters
OL,8,Fwhich are used for crime will be
OL,9,Fdestroyed by Hampshire and Isle of
OL,10,FWight Constabulary as part of a new
OL,11,Finitiative.
OL,13,FOperation Crush is the force's new
OL,14,Fapproach to dealing with crime,
OL,15,Fantisocial behaviour and high-risk
OL,16,Friding of electrically powered two-
OL,17,Fwheeled vehicles.
