OL,3,CElectric motorcycles and e-scooters
OL,4,Cused for crime to be destroyed by
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FInspector Andy Tester from Hampshire
OL,8,Fand Isle of Wight Roads Policing Unit
OL,9,Fsays electric motorcycles have been
OL,10,Fused over the last few years for crime
OL,11,Fand antisocial behaviour.
OL,13,FSome people using them wearing
OL,14,Fbalaclavas and carry weapons such as
OL,15,Fknives, axes and chainsaws. They are
OL,16,Falso used for drug crime.
OL,18,FPolice officers will now seize these
OL,19,Felectric motorcycles and destroy them
OL,20,Fif they are involved in criminal
OL,21,Factivity.
