OL,3,CElectric motorcycles and e-scooters
OL,4,Cused for crime to be destroyed by
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FInspector Tester said: "Our new
OL,8,Fapproach is once we get hold of these
OL,9,Fvehicles is not to give them back to
OL,10,Fthe people who have been committing
OL,11,Fcrime on them.
OL,13,F"What we're going to do differently
OL,14,Ffrom now on, is we're going to seize
OL,15,Fthese vehicles and we're going to
OL,16,Fdestroy them. So we take away the
OL,17,Fmeans of people committing these
OL,18,Foffences."
