OL,4,Cused for crime to be destroyed by
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FElectric bikes and e-scooters used for
OL,8,Fcrime will also be seized and
OL,9,Fdestroyed.
OL,11,FThe force said some electric bikes
OL,12,Fhave been modified to go faster than
OL,13,Fthey should, essentially becoming a
OL,14,Fmotorbike.
OL,16,FThey can be ridden dangerously and
OL,17,Fused to commit crime.
OL,19,FAcross the country, there are hundreds
OL,20,Fof thousands of e-scooters being used
OL,21,Fon the roads.
