OL,3,CElectric motorcycles and e-scooters
OL,4,Cused for crime to be destroyed by
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FHowever, using them outside of
OL,8,Forganised rental schemes and for
OL,9,Fprivate use is illegal.
OL,11,FSome people ride them on pavements
OL,12,Ftowards vulnerable pedestrians and
OL,13,Fcross roads in front of cars which can
OL,14,Fcause crashes.
OL,16,FPolice say where people are using any
OL,17,Fof these vehicles irresponsibly, they
OL,18,Fwill consider prosecuting the driver
OL,19,Ftoo.
